SELECT

	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_test_ods.`test_category`,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS TEST_CATEGORY,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_test_ods.`result_unit`,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS RESULT_UNIT,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_test_ods.`order_loinc`,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS ORDER_LOINC,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_test_ods.`result_loinc`,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS RESULT_LOINC,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_test_ods.`icd_10_code`,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS ICD_10_CODE,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(SRC_test_ods.`cpt_code`,char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS CPT_CODE,
	CAST(SRC_test_ods.phys_order_required AS SIGNED) AS VV_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(CAST('V4-TEST' AS CHAR),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS VV_SOURCE_SYSTEM
 FROM $DO_GHL1_MY_BOLD_ODS_TEST_ODS SRC_test_ods 

WHERE SRC_test_ods.test_pid IS NOT NULL AND SRC_test_ods.is_current = 1

WITH  EXPR_NAME_TEST 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_test_ods.VV_SOURCE_SYSTEM  AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_test_ods.test_pid AS VARCHAR(50))) AS V_TEST_PID
	,TRIM(SRC_test_ods.test_name ) AS V_TEST_NAME
	,TRIM(SRC_test_ods.test_category ) AS V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,TRIM(SRC_test_ods.cpt_code ) AS V_CPT_CODE
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_test_ods.icd_10_code AS VARCHAR(50))) AS V_ICD_10_CODE
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_test_ods.result_loinc AS VARCHAR(50))) AS V_RESULT_LOINC
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_test_ods.result_unit AS VARCHAR(50))) AS V_RESULT_UNIT
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_test_ods.order_loinc as VARCHAR(50))) AS V_ORDER_LOINC
	,SRC_test_ods.VV_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED  AS V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
 FROM 
	$TFORM_SRC_test_ods SRC_test_ods
 ), EXPR_NAME_VACCINE 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_vaccine_ods.VV_SOURCE_SYSTEM  AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_ods.vaccine_pid  AS VARCHAR(50))) AS V_TEST_PID
	,SRC_vaccine_ods.vaccine_name AS V_TEST_NAME
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_CPT_CODE
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_ICD_10_CODE
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_RESULT_LOINC
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_RESULT_UNIT
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_ORDER_LOINC
	,0 AS V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
 FROM 
	$TFORM_SRC_vaccine_ods SRC_vaccine_ods
 ), EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_encounter_ods.VV_SOURCE_SYSTEM  AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_encounter_ods.encounter_pid AS CHAR)) AS V_TEST_PID
	,SRC_encounter_ods.encounter_name AS V_TEST_NAME
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_CPT_CODE
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_ICD_10_CODE
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_RESULT_LOINC
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_RESULT_UNIT
	,CAST('' AS CHAR) AS V_ORDER_LOINC
	,0 AS V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
 FROM 
	$TFORM_SRC_encounter_ods SRC_encounter_ods
 ), VENN_GRP_NAME AS 
( 
	SELECT 
	EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_TEST_PID AS V_TEST_PID
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_TEST_NAME AS V_TEST_NAME
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_TEST_CATEGORY AS V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_CPT_CODE AS V_CPT_CODE
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_ICD_10_CODE AS V_ICD_10_CODE
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_RESULT_LOINC AS V_RESULT_LOINC
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_RESULT_UNIT AS V_RESULT_UNIT
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_ORDER_LOINC AS V_ORDER_LOINC
	,EXPR_NAME_TEST.V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED AS V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
	FROM 
		EXPR_NAME_TEST 

Union 
	SELECT 
	EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_TEST_PID AS V_TEST_PID
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_TEST_NAME AS V_TEST_NAME
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_TEST_CATEGORY AS V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_CPT_CODE AS V_CPT_CODE
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_ICD_10_CODE AS V_ICD_10_CODE
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_RESULT_LOINC AS V_RESULT_LOINC
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_RESULT_UNIT AS V_RESULT_UNIT
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_ORDER_LOINC AS V_ORDER_LOINC
	,EXPR_NAME_VACCINE.V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED AS V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
 	FROM 
		EXPR_NAME_VACCINE 
 
Union 
	SELECT 
	EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_TEST_PID AS V_TEST_PID
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_TEST_NAME AS V_TEST_NAME
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_TEST_CATEGORY AS V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_CPT_CODE AS V_CPT_CODE
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_ICD_10_CODE AS V_ICD_10_CODE
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_RESULT_LOINC AS V_RESULT_LOINC
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_RESULT_UNIT AS V_RESULT_UNIT
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_ORDER_LOINC AS V_ORDER_LOINC
	,EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER.V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED AS V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
 	FROM 
		EXPR_NAME_ENCOUNTER 
 ) 
,  EXPR_NAME 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	VENN_GRP_NAME.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_TEST_PID AS V_TEST_PID
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_TEST_NAME AS V_TEST_NAME
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_TEST_CATEGORY AS V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_CPT_CODE AS V_CPT_CODE
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_ICD_10_CODE AS V_ICD_10_CODE
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_RESULT_LOINC AS V_RESULT_LOINC
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_RESULT_UNIT AS V_RESULT_UNIT
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_ORDER_LOINC AS V_ORDER_LOINC
	,VENN_GRP_NAME.V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED AS V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CREATED_AT
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS UPDATED_AT
	,0 AS IS_DELETED
	,($SP_MAX_KEY.max_key  + row_number() OVER (ORDER BY (select 1))) AS TEST_KEY
 FROM 
	VENN_GRP_NAME
)MERGE $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_TEST TGT_dim_test 
 USING EXPR_NAME EXPR_NAME 
  ON TGT_dim_test.source_system = EXPR_NAME.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM AND 
TGT_dim_test.test_pid = EXPR_NAME.V_TEST_PID
 WHEN MATCHED THEN 
UPDATE SET
	test_name = EXPR_NAME.V_TEST_NAME
	,test_category = EXPR_NAME.V_TEST_CATEGORY
	,cpt_code = EXPR_NAME.V_CPT_CODE
	,icd10 = EXPR_NAME.V_ICD_10_CODE
	,result_loinc = EXPR_NAME.V_RESULT_LOINC
	,result_unit = EXPR_NAME.V_RESULT_UNIT
	,order_loinc = EXPR_NAME.V_ORDER_LOINC
	,phys_order_required = EXPR_NAME.V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED
	,created_at = EXPR_NAME.CREATED_AT
	,updated_at = EXPR_NAME.UPDATED_AT
	,is_deleted = EXPR_NAME.IS_DELETED
 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
INSERT
(test_key,test_pid,test_name,test_category,cpt_code,icd10,result_loinc,result_unit,order_loinc,phys_order_required,source_system,created_at,updated_at,is_deleted)
VALUES (
EXPR_NAME.TEST_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.V_TEST_PID,
EXPR_NAME.V_TEST_NAME,
EXPR_NAME.V_TEST_CATEGORY,
EXPR_NAME.V_CPT_CODE,
EXPR_NAME.V_ICD_10_CODE,
EXPR_NAME.V_RESULT_LOINC,
EXPR_NAME.V_RESULT_UNIT,
EXPR_NAME.V_ORDER_LOINC,
EXPR_NAME.V_PHYS_ORDER_REQUIRED,
EXPR_NAME.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM,
EXPR_NAME.CREATED_AT,
EXPR_NAME.UPDATED_AT,
EXPR_NAME.IS_DELETED)#SEMICOLON_DELIM#
